nter holds up the shield and sword parts of their Charge Blade.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt=\" A hunter holds up the shield and sword parts of their Charge Blade.\" data-link-reference=\"\" data-link-target=\"\" data-syndicationrights=\"true\" data-imagerights=\"fair-use\" data-hide=\"false\" data-hidecredit=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(max-width: 49.94em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_965/6a79901152555f0607a0bd03a9149ebf.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 50em) and (max-width: 63.69em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1315/6a79901152555f0607a0bd03a9149ebf.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 63.75em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1600/6a79901152555f0607a0bd03a9149ebf.jpg\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\" A hunter holds up the shield and sword parts of their Charge Blade.\" data-chomp-id=\"6a79901152555f0607a0bd03a9149ebf\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-height=\"1080\" data-alt=\" A hunter holds up the shield and sword parts of their Charge Blade.\" data-anim-src=\"\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/6a79901152555f0607a0bd03a9149ebf.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eScreenshot: Capcom / Kotaku\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cspan data-id=\"6a79901152555f0607a0bd03a9149ebf\" data-recommend-id=\"image://6a79901152555f0607a0bd03a9149ebf\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\" A hunter holds up the shield and sword parts of their Charge Blade.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eAlthough the Charge Blade is arguably the coolest weapon in \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/monster-hunter-wilds-review-ps5-open-world-rpg-capcom-1851766113\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/monster-hunter-wilds-review-ps5-open-world-rpg-capcom-1851766113\"\u003e\u003cem\u003eMonster Hunter Wilds\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e, it’s also one of the most complicated. You need to understand both of its modes \u003cem\u003eand\u003c/em\u003e the unique mechanics to use it properly. That’s asking for a lot when compared with other weapons in the game, but we promise the damage it delivers makes this worth the extra effort. - Samuel Moreno \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/monster-hunter-wilds-best-weapon-the-charge-blade-guide-1851769340\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/monster-hunter-wilds-best-weapon-the-charge-blade-guide-1851769340\"\u003eRead More\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure id=\"\" data-id=\"eedf124b83aa28782d437c348d99095b\" data-recommend-id=\"image://eedf124b83aa28782d437c348d99095b\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"An overhead view of a fledgling Roma in Civilization VII.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt=\"An overhead view of a fledgling Roma in Civilization VII.\" data-link-reference=\"\" data-link-target=\"\" data-syndicationrights=\"true\" data-imagerights=\"fair-use\" data-hide=\"false\" data-hidecredit=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(max-width: 49.94em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_965/eedf124b83aa28782d437c348d99095b.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 50em) and (max-width: 63.69em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1315/eedf124b83aa28782d437c348d99095b.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 63.75em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1600/eedf124b83aa28782d437c348d99095b.jpg\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"An overhead view of a fledgling Roma in Civilization VII.\" data-chomp-id=\"eedf124b83aa28782d437c348d99095b\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-height=\"1080\" data-alt=\"An overhead view of a fledgling Roma in Civilization VII.\" data-anim-src=\"\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/eedf124b83aa28782d437c348d99095b.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eScreenshot: Firaxis Games / Kotaku\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cspan data-id=\"eedf124b83aa28782d437c348d99095b\" data-recommend-id=\"image://eedf124b83aa28782d437c348d99095b\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"An overhead view of a fledgling Roma in Civilization VII.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eAs you begin to step beyond your boundaries and expand your empire in \u003cem\u003eCivilization VII\u003c/em\u003e, you’ll note that investing in a Settler and sending them off on a mission to settle new land doesn’t culminate in a city like previous entries. You begin with a township. A town is a small settlement, held back by its size, incapable of fielding multiple specialists or building certain structures. But it’s your footprint on the world. - Brandon Morgan \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/civ-7-civilization-vii-how-to-upgrade-towns-cities-1851769615\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/civ-7-civilization-vii-how-to-upgrade-towns-cities-1851769615\"\u003eRead More\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure id=\"\" data-id=\"ea8f460bc3151a75cab5115873acd389\" data-recommend-id=\"image://ea8f460bc3151a75cab5115873acd389\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"A selection of cards from Pocket on a pretty background.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt=\"A selection of cards from Pocket on a pretty background.\" data-link-reference=\"\" data-link-target=\"\" data-syndicationrights=\"true\" data-imagerights=\"fair-use\" data-hide=\"false\" data-hidecredit=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(max-width: 49.94em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_965/ea8f460bc3151a75cab5115873acd389.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 50em) and (max-width: 63.69em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1315/ea8f460bc3151a75cab5115873acd389.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 63.75em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1600/ea8f460bc3151a75cab5115873acd389.jpg\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"A selection of cards from Pocket on a pretty background.\" data-chomp-id=\"ea8f460bc3151a75cab5115873acd389\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-height=\"1080\" data-alt=\"A selection of cards from Pocket on a pretty background.\" data-anim-src=\"\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/ea8f460bc3151a75cab5115873acd389.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eImage: The Pokémon Company / Kotaku\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cspan data-id=\"ea8f460bc3151a75cab5115873acd389\" data-recommend-id=\"im